item.title: About me
item.description: Hello, I’m Jae 😁 🔭 I’m working as TD in Vancouver, especially focusing on the lighting. I also keep learning CS and Math to be a better engineer in the industry through the materials from everywhere. All of this journey started from a tiny step of python scripting while working as lighter. Hope that I can go deeper inside and contribute for the artists, industry and the communities. 💬 Ask anything about me via Linkedin!
